msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/config-tls-mattermost.rst:11
msgid "**Configure TLS on the Mattermost Server**:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/config-tls-mattermost.rst:13
msgid ""
"In the **System Console** > **General** > **Configuration** in prior "
"versions or **System Console** > **Environment** > **Web Server** in "
"versions after 5.12."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/config-tls-mattermost.rst:14
msgid "Change the **Listen Address** setting to ``:443``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/config-tls-mattermost.rst:15
msgid "Change the **Connection Security** setting to ``TLS``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/config-tls-mattermost.rst:16
msgid "Change the **Forward port 80 to 443** setting to ``true``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/config-tls-mattermost.rst:17
msgid ""
"Activate the ``CAP_NET_BIND_SERVICE`` capability to allow Mattermost to "
"bind to low ports."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/config-tls-mattermost.rst:19
msgid "``sudo setcap cap_net_bind_service=+ep /opt/mattermost/bin/mattermost``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/config-tls-mattermost.rst:21
msgid ""
"Install the security certificate. You can use `Let's Encrypt "
"<https://letsencrypt.org/>`__ to automatically install and setup the "
"certificate, or you can specify your own certificate."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/config-tls-mattermost.rst:23
msgid "**To use a Let's Encrypt certificate**:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/config-tls-mattermost.rst:25
msgid ""
"The certificate is retrieved the first time that a client tries to "
"connect to the Mattermost server. Certificates are retrieved for any "
"hostname a client tries to reach the server at."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/config-tls-mattermost.rst:27
msgid "Change the **Use Let's Encrypt** setting to ``true``."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/config-tls-mattermost.rst:28
#: ../../source/install/config-tls-mattermost.rst:38
msgid "Restart the Mattermost server for these changes to take effect."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/install/config-tls-mattermost.rst:31
msgid ""
"If Let's Encrypt is enabled, forward port 80 through a firewall, with "
"`Forward80To443 <https://docs.mattermost.com/administration/config-"
"settings.html#forward-port-80-to-443>`__ ``config.json`` setting set to "
"``true`` to complete the Let's Encrypt certification."
msgstr ""

